{
  "stem": "3804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember that when I was separated from this-- from [INAUDIBLE], and I separate from my other friends there, the brother-- the uncle-- my uncle and all this, I said, I remember this small girl.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She said to me-- She gave me some handkerchief.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she said, take it and remember me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I said, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she said because we are not going to see each other anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I said, why not?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had been small children, but still we have already felt the-- the sorry and the grief.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We-- we lived it that we are, how do you say, somebody is-- is looking-- want our life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Something is unstable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And mostly we look at-- I [? held ?] the cross between my mother and father, why to leave.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I ask my rabbi first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the rabbi always-- And I have to blame a lot, the rabbis at the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They say, you have bread?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You live.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Why do you care?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Why do you have to go to Israel and start a new life?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And my mother said, I don't want to hear the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I want to hear everything-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We leave.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So, you know, a lot of people, it was not just like go, leave the country and go, they have to ask their rabbi.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They have to ask their authority, like the authority, can we go?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "What will happen?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they always said, easy, if the God will, if they want.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "How to say, if God will, you can stay everywhere, anywhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Why do you have to change your life?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You-- you are accustomed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You have your community and all this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of people listened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of people listened.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
